      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Attention DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! Here is a great opportunity to pick up a vehicle with tons of potential at a budget-friendly price. While it currently needs some significant mechanical attention and cosmetic work, it serves as a solid foundation for someone handy who loves a restoration project. It's being sold as-is, perfect for those looking for a diamond in the rough to bring back to its former glory!",
