    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is sound with a smooth engine and transmission, and all major systems are functioning as they should. The exterior is clean, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and light wear consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is tidy and smoke-free, showing only slight aging on the driver's seat bolster. It\u2019s a reliable choice for someone looking for a quality car that is ready for the road.",
